"tid":1123932,"uid":94828,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"糖尿病分兩種 後天個種係因為身體對胰島素冇反應<br />\n中三bio冇學過？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"吓？<br />\n你所謂後天係咪T2DM?<br />\nT2DM食oral唔掂要打insulin㗎喎<br />\n你識唔識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"type 1先係打胰島素wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:42:07.000Z","msg":"Type 1 type2都可以打insulin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nT2姐係上面位人兄講後天嗰種<br />\n通當食oral如metformin sglt2 dpp4i都唔掂<br />\n就會打insulin<br />\nT2dm並唔係條友所講後天對insulin冇反應<br />\n利申有中三以上bio水平"},{"pid":"f10fa77259505c9c879255928d73e12275788f89","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"26a6c5a25b1ae654f6c1c1026aff8a0c5b20db41","tid":1123932,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2d64b7a7b7d15fcb7807174d62fed35ffb772eae","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"36d0638137175a23b44611d97277967470883354","tid":1123932,"uid":94828,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T18:52:41.000Z","msg":"糖尿病分兩種 後天個種係因為身體對胰島素冇反應<br />\n中三bio冇學過？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"吓？<br />\n你所謂後天係咪T2DM?<br />\nT2DM食oral唔掂要打insulin㗎喎<br />\n你識唔識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"自己上網查多次啦<br />\n問人識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"臨床上，將糖尿病分成四類:<br />\n1. 第1型糖尿病(type 1 diabetes, T1DM):由於&beta;細<br />\n胞的損害，導致絕對的胰島素缺乏。<br />\n2. 第2型糖尿病(type 2 diabetes, T2DM):由於胰島<br />\n素阻抗，造成胰島素分泌的持續缺陷。<br />\n3. 因其他系統疾病而引發的糖尿病，例如&beta;細胞功 能，或胰島素作用的基因缺陷，胰臟外分泌疾病 (如:囊性纖維化)，由於藥物或化學物品引起的<br />\n糖尿病(如:治療AIDS過程，或器官移植之後)。<br />\n4. 妊娠糖尿病:在妊娠過程中出現的糖尿病。<br />\n<br />\n粗啲講<br />\n一型就係先天beta壞令到冇insulin<br />\n二型就後天食得太肥個胰臟扯得太盡令到唔夠使<br />\n無論係一型定係二型甚至係講緊第三四種併發症<br />\n都係講緊胰島素嘅缺乏<br />\n而唔係你所謂身體對胰島素冇反應<br />\n打胰島素係對於一型二型糖尿病都有用<br />\n你中三bio阿sir教你錯嘢定係你唔識扮識？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tma.tw%2Fltk%2F99530904.pdf&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0rTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=aba929dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"0f22220fe36f4e676fea5f7d67c9bcd037077453","tid":1123932,"uid":198866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f10fa77259505c9c879255928d73e12275788f89","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"26a6c5a25b1ae654f6c1c1026aff8a0c5b20db41","tid":1123932,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2d64b7a7b7d15fcb7807174d62fed35ffb772eae","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"吓？<br />\n你所謂後天係咪T2DM?<br />\nT2DM食oral唔掂要打insulin㗎喎<br />\n你識唔識㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"自己上網查多次啦<br />\n問人識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"臨床上，將糖尿病分成四類:<br />\n1. 第1型糖尿病(type 1 diabetes, T1DM):由於&beta;細<br />\n胞的損害，導致絕對的胰島素缺乏。<br />\n2. 第2型糖尿病(type 2 diabetes, T2DM):由於胰島<br />\n素阻抗，造成胰島素分泌的持續缺陷。<br />\n3. 因其他系統疾病而引發的糖尿病，例如&beta;細胞功 能，或胰島素作用的基因缺陷，胰臟外分泌疾病 (如:囊性纖維化)，由於藥物或化學物品引起的<br />\n糖尿病(如:治療AIDS過程，或器官移植之後)。<br />\n4. 妊娠糖尿病:在妊娠過程中出現的糖尿病。<br />\n<br />\n粗啲講<br />\n一型就係先天beta壞令到冇insulin<br />\n二型就後天食得太肥個胰臟扯得太盡令到唔夠使<br />\n無論係一型定係二型甚至係講緊第三四種併發症<br />\n都係講緊胰島素嘅缺乏<br />\n而唔係你所謂身體對胰島素冇反應<br />\n打胰島素係對於一型二型糖尿病都有用<br />\n你中三bio阿sir教你錯嘢定係你唔識扮識？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tma.tw%2Fltk%2F99530904.pdf&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0rTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=aba929dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"Check up from American diabetes association. <br />\n<br />\nFor type2 diabetes, insulin resistance comes first, and then what you mentioned happen but the root problem is still insulin resistance. Also, no one can tell the real cause of type 2 diabetes, overweight is just a risk factor, so your statements are wrong and misleading.<br />\n<br />\nPlease do fact check.<br />\n<br />\nP.s. My form 3 bio teacher did not tell me anything, thanks."},{"pid":"855552ace4800edc1389bc1a4390cd4dfdef88a3","tid":1123932,"uid":250550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"應該咁講 (括號嘢只係補充下啲書料)<br />\nT1DM係先天 (pathophysiology 係 Type 4 hypersensitivity reaction, autoimmune destruction of pancreatic islet) <br />\nT2DM係後天 係insulin resistance, 背後有好多risk factors<br />\nT2DM 食藥(oral hypoglycemic drug) 其中一種係增加 insulin secretion (endogenous)<br />\nT1DM T2DM兩者都可以打insulin (exogenous)<br />\n有Resistance 所以多啲 insulin 先有足夠effect <br />\n無人話過有resistance = insulin 完全冇用"},{"pid":"766ab00a0551c79884f7c0b25ca4f8cfc1367cf0","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f22220fe36f4e676fea5f7d67c9bcd037077453","tid":1123932,"uid":198866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f10fa77259505c9c879255928d73e12275788f89","tid":1123932,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"26a6c5a25b1ae654f6c1c1026aff8a0c5b20db41","tid":1123932,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"自己上網查多次啦<br />\n問人識唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"臨床上，將糖尿病分成四類:<br />\n1. 第1型糖尿病(type 1 diabetes, T1DM):由於&beta;細<br />\n胞的損害，導致絕對的胰島素缺乏。<br />\n2. 第2型糖尿病(type 2 diabetes, T2DM):由於胰島<br />\n素阻抗，造成胰島素分泌的持續缺陷。<br />\n3. 因其他系統疾病而引發的糖尿病，例如&beta;細胞功 能，或胰島素作用的基因缺陷，胰臟外分泌疾病 (如:囊性纖維化)，由於藥物或化學物品引起的<br />\n糖尿病(如:治療AIDS過程，或器官移植之後)。<br />\n4. 妊娠糖尿病:在妊娠過程中出現的糖尿病。<br />\n<br />\n粗啲講<br />\n一型就係先天beta壞令到冇insulin<br />\n二型就後天食得太肥個胰臟扯得太盡令到唔夠使<br />\n無論係一型定係二型甚至係講緊第三四種併發症<br />\n都係講緊胰島素嘅缺乏<br />\n而唔係你所謂身體對胰島素冇反應<br />\n打胰島素係對於一型二型糖尿病都有用<br />\n你中三bio阿sir教你錯嘢定係你唔識扮識？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tma.tw%2Fltk%2F99530904.pdf&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0rTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=aba929dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.tma.tw/ltk/99530904.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"Check up from American diabetes association. <br />\n<br />\nFor type2 diabetes, insulin resistance comes first, and then what you mentioned happen but the root problem is still insulin resistance. Also, no one can tell the real cause of type 2 diabetes, overweight is just a risk factor, so your statements are wrong and misleading.<br />\n<br />\nPlease do fact check.<br />\n<br />\nP.s. My form 3 bio teacher did not tell me anything, thanks."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T18:24:08.000Z","msg":"Resistance就係冇反應?<br />\n你對insulin sensitivity低<br />\n正常level都唔夠你用<br />\n咪啫係insulin deficiency囉<br />\nDM佬見你resist咪一樣用sufonylurea 嗰類oral/injection整到夠insulin去control hba1c 同fasting glucose<br />\n並唔係好似條友講冇反應囉"},{"pid":"740a68717bdc18cd00a021b987c3aa3a517b1c83","tid":1123932,"uid":98100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T19:12:19.000Z","msg":"笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只可以講<br />\n咁一般DM2 patient 要打幾多噸insulin 先可以有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntheoretically speaking, u may be right<br />\nBut I hate your attitude<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}